# =============================================================================
# assets/sprites/.gitignore
# =============================================================================
# Excludes generated sprite sheet PNG images. These are produced by
# sprite_sheets.py during extraction and can be regenerated from the ROM.
# Developers can also edit these PNGs and use --sprites-from-png to compile
# modified sprites back into the asset file.
# =============================================================================

# All generated sprite sheet PNGs (per-character and master tilesheets)
/*.png
